snippet.title: Taram Baba Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Plunge your light deeper and deeper into the darkness of the abyss and fight your way to Taram Baba.

Taram Baba is an Action Roguelike that focuses on lightning-fast combat mechanics.
Feel every blow you land on evil while you fight your way through the haunting abyss. Chase Taram Baba deeper and deeper into the dark and cling to your light, for the walls are moving.

Try Taram Baba Demo on Steam!

Link to the demo: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3516750/Taram_Baba_Demo/

Wishlist the full game;
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3420790/Taram_Baba/
